item.title: Delta source questions
item.dc:creator: @vManlyMan vManlyMan
item.description:
@vManlyMan wrote:

To make items stronger.

  1. Open item.cfg
  2. Search for your item.
  3. All those numbers right past the description are the bonuses.
  4. Change those to your liking.
